high_descs: go to sink to the right
pick up knife on back left side of sink
turn to counter on left with salt shakers
slice tomato to the right of salt shaker
go to sink to the right
place knife in left side of sink
go to counter to the right with tomato
pick up slice of tomato from counter
go to sink to the right
place tomato in right, front side of sink, turn on water, remove tomato slice from sink
go to refrigerator to the right, open refrigerator
place tomato slice on top shelf of refrigerator, close refrigerator
anns.task_desc: Place washed tomato slice on top shelf of refrigerator

high_descs: Turn right, walk to the sink.
Pick up knife from the sink.
Turn left, walk to the counter.
Cut the tomato on the counter.
Turn right, go to the sink.
Put the knife in the sink.
Turn left, go to the counter.
Pick up tomato slice from the counter.
Turn right, go to the sink.
Put the tomato slice in the sink, fill sink with water, empty sink, pick up tomato slice.
Turn right, walk to refrigerator, turn left to face refrigerator.
Put tomato on top shelf of refrigerator.
anns.task_desc: Put a slice of tomato in the refrigerator.

high_descs: Head forward then turn right and go to the kitchen sink.
Pick up the knife that is in the sink above the spoon.
Turn left and walk to the counter with the salt shakers.
Slice the tomato next to the salt shaker.
Turn around and go to the kitchen sink on the left.
Place the knife in the sink next to the spoon.
Turn left and return to the salt shakers counter.
Pick up a slice of tomato.
Turn right and return to the kitchen sink.
Place the tomato slice in the sink, turn on the faucet for a few seconds, then off, pick up the tomato.
Turn right and head towards the end of the hall, turn left to face the fridge.
Open the fridge, place tomato on top shelf, close fridge.
anns.task_desc: Place a slice of washed tomato into the fridge.
